>|> There is a scheme called LUC developed by a group in New Zealand. There 
>|> is some question as to how much of the original development was done by 
>|> them and how much was borrowed, but in any case it differs from RSA. It 
>|> is based on the use of Lucas sequences. The January 1993 Dr Dobb's 
